                      "ops": [
                        {
                          "insert": "1. Hard refresh: Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows) or Cmd+Shift+R (Mac). 2. Clear browser cache and cookies. 3. Try incognito mode. 4. Disable browser extensions. 5. Try a different browser. If none work, check our status page at status.example.com.",
